睇雷霆傘兵</blockquote><br />\n依套屌打哂所有戰爭片啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nband of Brothers 係最好<br />\n不過樓主係講電影定包埋電視劇?<br />\n<br />\n如果無限制PK點都係BoB<br />\n 如果只限現代戰爭可以睇吓Generation Kill, Black Hawk Down"},{"pid":"f25295c8e25b1d3dc4e9b93efeb4a438027c7e05","tid":503721,"uid":47147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T07:29:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"38ee9a1f9744561c40748b5df0e4274ab1c0818f","tid":503721,"uid":38425,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T07:30:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>德國劇 我們的父輩有得揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無人睇？ 呢套仲殘酷過Ryan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我無睇過, 大概講的乜?</blockquote><br />\n講一班後生德國仔女係二戰入面唔同既命運，主角兩兄弟去左當兵，有個猶太人老死，一個立志當軍醫既女仔朋友同一個發明星夢既女性朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 從一個普通德國人角度去拍呢套戲，最好睇係當兵兩兄弟既故事，最後細佬完完全全演到明知祖國打緊敗伏，但仍然要出去送死個種現實殘酷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a0fe8cd59a18bd8e8ab923ac9cedcc247a7fbd","tid":503721,"uid":18417,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T07:30:32.000Z","msg":"其實係好好睇， 但 最近既 Dunkirk 真係拍得幾好， 希望今年Nolan 可以攞oscar"},{"pid":"4d5a3c6020edeeee44c5f80f756acd2a1fbd9302","tid":503721,"uid":134834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T07:31:26.000Z","msg":"敵對邊緣屌打雷霆救兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9334194b83b2d32ede3ce18291853ac4f92714ea","tid":503721,"uid":97267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T07:35:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我寧願睇雷霆傘兵</blockquote><br />\n不用分那麼細 反正都係史匹堡作品<br />\n兩套都應該睇"},{"pid":"2ab6f34e636dd8e7545831f81f9e8ac253db7fdf","tid":503721,"uid":35231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT